{"tid":906160,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"金搖桿獎《Fornite》擊敗《碧血狂殺2》獲GOTY年度最佳遊戲","createTime":"2018-11-17T17:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T11:18:04.000Z","uid":89160,"like":21,"dislike":218,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"cec46677cbcbbf84c598e020c690956eafb45a72","tid":906160,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:28:42.000Z","msg":"搶在 The Game Awards（TGA）頒獎之前，另一個年度遊戲業界肯定獎項「金搖桿獎」（Golden Joystick Awards）獲獎名單於今（17）日出爐，外界普便看好《碧血狂殺 2》（Red Dead Redemption 2）並未拿下「GOTY」（Game of the Year）年度最佳遊戲，而是由風靡全球的《Fortnite》拿下。<br />\n<br />\n2018 年許多大作傾巢而出，這些耳熟能詳的 3A 大作幾乎都榜上有名，只是令人意外的是，獨立遊戲《深海迷航》（Subnautica）能擊敗眾家大廠獲得年度最家 PC Game 獎項與最佳突破獎項殊榮，其假探索之名實為恐怖冒險遊戲，真的實至名歸。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，一改過去戰鬥風格的《戰神》以描述克雷多斯當爸的冒險獲得最佳故事獎、PlayStation 年度最佳遊戲、最佳視覺設計獎、最佳音效等獎項，還讓 Santa Monica 工作室獲得年度最佳團隊。<br />\n<br />\n其他榜上有名的大作也同樣獲獎肯定，像是《極限競速：地平線 4》則為 Xbox 年度最佳遊戲，《八方旅人》為 Nintendo 年度最佳遊戲。另外，卡普空狩獵名作《魔物獵人 世界》獲最佳合作遊戲獎，《戰車世界》獲至今還在玩的遊戲長青獎，《底特律：變人》拿下最佳表演獎，《死亡細胞》則是拿下最佳獨立遊戲獎。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，過去橫掃多項獎項的《絕地求生》，今年氣勢較不如去年，僅拿下年度最佳手遊獎，反倒是主要競爭對手《Fortnite》拿下了最佳電子競技獎與年度最佳遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n當然，最期待遊戲獎，自然是 CD Projekt RED 今年釋出實機宣傳的《電馭叛客 2077》，相信這是無庸至疑的。至於備受好評的《碧血狂殺 2》，則拿下了評審遊戲獎。<br />\n<br />\n以下為本屆金搖桿所有獎項名單：<br />\n<br />\nBest Storytelling：《戰神》<br />\nStudio of the Year： Sony Santa Monica<br />\nBest New Streamer/Broadcaster：Amelia Rose Blaire 與 Bryan Dechart<br />\nMobile Game of the Year：《絕地求生》<br />\nBest Competitive Game：《Fortnite》（堡壘之夜 / 要塞英雄）<br />\nPC Game of the Year：《深海迷航》<br />\nPlayStation Game of the Year：《戰神》<br />\nBest Co-op Game：《魔物獵人 世界》<br />\nXbox Game of the Year：《極限競速：地平線 4》<br />\nBest Visual Design：《戰神》<br />\nNintendo Game of the Year：《八方旅人》<br />\nBest Indie Game：《死亡細胞》<br />\nBreakthrough Award：《深海迷航》<br />\nMost Wanted Game：《電馭叛客 2077》<br />\nCritics Choice Award：《碧血狂殺 2》<br />\nBest Audio：《戰神》<br />\nStill Playing Award：《戰車世界》<br />\nBest Performer：Bryan Dechart（Detroit: Become Human）<br />\nOutstanding Contribution：Microsoft（Xbox 無障礙控制器）<br />\nBest VR Game：《上古卷軸 無界天際 VR》（Skyrim VR）<br />\nGame of the Year：《Fortnite》（堡壘之夜 / 要塞英雄）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/37098/fortnite-beats-out-red-dead-redemption-2-for-golden-joysticks-game-of-the-year\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F37098%2Ffortnite-beats-out-red-dead-redemption-2-for-golden-joysticks-game-of-the-year&d=Iy8f23t4%2Be1Fh2T7qfBAiL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=789de982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/37098/fortnite-beats-out-red-dead-redemption-2-for-golden-joysticks-game-of-the-year</a>"},{"pid":"93bfa6282d8cb9bfc116efbd3e09c75d0a5f942c","tid":906160,"uid":179467,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:30:13.000Z","msg":"Fortnite我覺得好有機會同Overwatch一樣命運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8237d4d1bab1e397c61bb56e14ab6a28991164b8","tid":906160,"uid":24737,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:32:09.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"fbc0b2bc2fab740256f12b74c1a9be154869ed28","tid":906160,"uid":46538,"like":77,"dislike":15,"score":62,"quote":{"pid":"93bfa6282d8cb9bfc116efbd3e09c75d0a5f942c","tid":906160,"uid":179467,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:30:13.000Z","msg":"Fortnite我覺得好有機會同Overwatch一樣命運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:34:46.000Z","msg":"overwatch, 要比錢之後又少update <br />\nfortnite 唔洗錢又成日出新野 新玩法<br />\n<br />\n利申fortnite 課battle pass"},{"pid":"c83c49a7ccbcdeefc9e65b93974721a86492364a","tid":906160,"uid":1425,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:36:07.000Z","msg":"tga&gt;&gt;&gt;golden joystick"},{"pid":"84eaf155ce923b4e5dbbcb106fb217e7daa700c3","tid":906160,"uid":7508,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:36:11.000Z","msg":"太公分豬肉咁<img src=\"/as